"      Rytmocard (BG, PH);",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Rytmonorm (BE, CH, CL, CZ, DE, DK, EE, ES, FI, HK, HN, HR, HU, ID, IT, JO, KP, LU, MY, NL, NZ, PE, PL, PT, RU, SE, SG, TH, TR, TW, UY, VE);",
