"     Peter F Weller, MD, FACP",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials contributorType\" href=\"./treatment-of-cutaneous-leishmaniasis/contributors\">",
